HEADWORD: Yelting
<hw>Yel"ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Orig. uncert.]</ety>
<def>The Florida and West Indian red snapper (<spn>Lutianus aya</spn>);
also, sometimes, one of certain other allied species, as <spn>Lutianus
caxis</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
